cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.HC, cs.GR 

The paper discusses sketch recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes an active learning framework, which involves machine learning algorithms (cs.AI) and optimization techniques (cs.LG). The paper also discusses user interaction and annotation, which falls under human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Finally, the paper discusses the segmentation of sketches, which is a topic in computer graphics (cs.GR).
